item.title: aUstin Haga- Changes (AK Remix)
item.dc:creator: AnirudhKhanna
item.description:
Oh, I’m very sorry for using the artwork… I’ll change that. I respect your feedback. I realize I didn’t really add loops in, but that was mainly because I like to add a lot of loops, and I ran out of space building the drums, and I would add melody, it was just that I couldn’t find any melody that would fit your incredibly original sound.
